{"tid":1298434,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［有消息］728 將軍澳反送中大遊行","createTime":"2019-07-09T01:22:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T05:57:58.000Z","uid":1251,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"76fdad94bee2cb976bb9025c1b62eb6908ee48e7","tid":1298434,"uid":1251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T01:22:23.000Z","msg":"將軍澳街坊搞既遊行出左新消息啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有關將軍澳人大遊行，最新消息如下：<br />\n<br />\n728 將軍澳反送中大遊行<br />\n<br />\n我們是一群民間自發，沒有任何政黨背景的將軍澳素人。不撤不散，十八區遍地開花，將軍澳人決定召集728 將軍澳反送中大遊行。<br />\n<br />\n日期：7月28日<br />\n<br />\n遊行路線 (待定，正申請不反對通知書)：寶翠公園 -&gt; 寶林北路 (經將軍澳警署對出) -&gt; 寶寧路 -&gt; 將軍澳政府綜合大樓 -&gt; 坑口文曲里連儂牆 -&gt; 將軍澳單車館公園<br />\n<br />\n1. 遊行目的<br />\n<br />\n重申五大訴求：<br />\n<br />\n徹底撤回修例<br />\n<br />\n收回暴動定義<br />\n<br />\n撤銷至今對所有反送中抗爭者控罪<br />\n<br />\n徹底追究警隊濫權情況<br />\n<br />\n以行政命令解散立法會，立即施實行雙普選<br />\n<br />\n有鑒於連日來有傳媒對抗爭者的抹黑，我們尊重新聞自由，但亦在此抗議媒體失實報導。希望傳媒作為具監察力量的第四權，秉持專業精神為市民作持平報導。<br />\n<br />\n2. 與「將軍澳7.21大遊行」之關係<br />\n<br />\n區政聯盟及將軍澳民生關注組 (下稱該政黨)所舉辦之「將軍澳7.21大遊行」，和我們並沒有任何關連。該政黨於7月7日發佈有關「將軍澳7.21大遊行」資訊之前，並未有與我們溝通，團隊亦毫不知情。該政黨曾潛伏於遊行籌備群組內，隱瞞其身份，令團隊對其目的存疑。我們考慮過與其溝通，但礙於該政黨有失誠信，最後決定放棄協調。因此我們重申，是次「728 將軍澳反送中大遊行」 是民間素人自發，拒絕為任何政黨作宣傳或選舉造勢。我們歡迎任何同路人同行，但請各政黨自重。<br />\n<br />\n3. 有關路線安排<br />\n<br />\n暫定路線不會途徑TVB。TVB位置遠離市中心，缺乏補給、退場路線。為保障當日遊行人士安全，商討後決定遊行集中於市中心。然而TVB對抗爭者的報導手法偏頗，將軍澳人絕不容忍，抗議傳媒失實報導仍作為主要訴求之一。<br />\n<br />\n今次遊行由Hang Ng於7月4日初次提議，到我們一班素人團隊組織起來商討，短短的一星期有賴各個將軍澳群組、連登巴絲的意見。團隊並無政黨支持，亦缺乏經驗，希望大家多多包涵，會繼續聆聽各方聲音。<br />\n<br />\n不撤不散，728見！<br />\n<br />\n一眾將軍澳人敬上<br />\n<br />\n2019年7月9日"},{"pid":"e30b6740538bf5c249f7dce433ecfb174675f2bd","tid":1298434,"uid":210778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T01:23:14.000Z","msg":"醬汁呢"},{"pid":"ae8a94c47a6010f8534cb452a97991e60001e733","tid":1298434,"uid":1251,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e30b6740538bf5c249f7dce433ecfb174675f2bd","tid":1298434,"uid":210778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T01:23:14.000Z","msg":"醬汁呢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T01:26:00.000Z","msg":"將軍澳FB group 係Closed group share唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f58ae6522e616cb4851bf4b5d0f7d4cbd3990544","tid":1298434,"uid":1251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T01:27:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V36y5Sg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV36y5Sg.png&h=2c09dff3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4d9283da61b536c68ceb68c43c634070d45905d9","tid":1298434,"uid":242393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T01:31:59.000Z","msg":"連續兩星期將軍澳可能係巧合<br />\n但希望都可以配合一下<br />\n例如於不同位置設置連儂牆"},{"pid":"337e9e5203c0bf75d4b3dfb91055e185d39fa762","tid":1298434,"uid":1251,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4d9283da61b536c68ceb68c43c634070d45905d9","tid":1298434,"uid":242393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T01:31:59.000Z","msg":"連續兩星期將軍澳可能係巧合<br />\n但希望都可以配合一下<br />\n例如於不同位置設置連儂牆"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T02:13:36.000Z","msg":"應該政棍搞721個會取消"},{"pid":"50cb04da225a66abd48915b515fee15d87b6c91f","tid":1298434,"uid":235089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4d9283da61b536c68ceb68c43c634070d45905d9","tid":1298434,"uid":242393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T01:31:59.000Z","msg":"連續兩星期將軍澳可能係巧合<br />\n但希望都可以配合一下<br />\n例如於不同位置設置連儂牆"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T02:41:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ndnqXoj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FndnqXoj.png&h=37d2d038&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"27d8af3740d8735903d366f83e47faa4a1730ed9","tid":1298434,"uid":1251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T05:23:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83865fa7bea0d4c9d792f0cc8685cb4c2a934d18","tid":1298434,"uid":6799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T05:30:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"36cf5114c230c1f4edb1ee344037988ce7b26392","tid":1298434,"uid":1251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T05:33:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8451a951ffab8f2ce8396be167e2db6af6958b5","tid":1298434,"uid":72859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T05:56:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/HqW3bQA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHqW3bQA.gif&h=219d0f9a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ece03bb705cc5571b66dd57c8bfaea2a0db4ae01","tid":1298434,"uid":129805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T05:57:58.000Z","msg":"推"}]}